A 45 cm tall cat sits 60 cm at the front of a concave mirror with a radius of curvature of 50 cm. What is the characteristics of the image formed?

options.a: A real, upright image with height 32.1 cm.
options.b: A virtual, upright image with height 13.2 cm.
options.c: A real, inverted image with height 32.1 cm.
options.d: A virtual, inverted image with height 32.1 cm.

correct_answer_text: A real, inverted image with height 32.1 cm.
